name: TextExpander Packs
body:
# TextExpander snippet packs for developers

## Packs available:
* Apache
* CSS, Sass
* Git, SVN (Subversion)
* Linux, Ubuntu, CentOS
* MySQL, SQL
* PHP
* Ruby
* Shell commands
* Drush (Drupal)


Project URL: http://github.com/ccharlton/TextExpander-Packs
